dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Addresses_2016.gdb.[This file contains point data representing buildings placed based upon aerial photography. The points are attributed with address information with both County names and 911 ani/ali verified names. The points are also attributed with emergency service numbers and municipality.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
